<span id="page_12">p. 12</span>

63\. Learn from me, in a concise form, O radiant goddess of the earth,
the eternal laws for the aggregate of the four castes, together with the
customs to be observed by each order, and with the secret ordinances,

64\. 'Which will effect the final liberation of the virtuous persons,
who will support thee. Be seated upon this splendid golden seat, O
handsome-thighed goddess.

65\. 'Seated at ease, listen to me proclaiming the sacred laws.' The
goddess of the earth, thereupon, seated at case, listened to the sacred
precepts as, they came from the mouth of Vish*n*u.

